强烈的[[东风波|东风波]]在2007年8月中旬离开非洲西海岸进入[[大西洋|北大西洋]]，拉开'''飓风迪安的气象历史'''序幕。东风波起初遭遇强烈的东向[[风切变|风切变]]，但快速进入适合[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]发展的环境后还是迅速组织，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]8月13日早上将位于[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]以东超过2400公里海域的天气系统归入热带低气压。

系统因北面的深层[[高压脊|高压脊]]转向西进并迅速进入[[加勒比地区|加勒比地区]]温暖水域。8月14日，低气压有所增强并升级热带风暴，美国国家飓风中心以“迪安”命名。8月16日风暴已达飓风标准。[[飓风迪安|飓风迪安]]在向西穿越小安的列斯群岛的过程中继续强化，一度在加勒比海中爆发性增强至[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的五级飓风强度。接下来飓风略有减弱，于8月19日以四级飓风强度在[[牙买加|牙买加]]南部海岸掠过后继续朝[[尤卡坦半岛|尤卡坦半岛]]水温更高的洋面进发。[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]西部的有利条件让风暴得以在次日再度强化并达到五级飓风标准，然后在[[金塔纳罗奥州|金塔纳罗奥州]][[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]。

飓风迪安是[[2007年大西洋飓风季|2007年大西洋飓风季]]期间以五级强度登陆过的两场风暴之一，并且与[[飓风卡米尔|飓风卡米尔]]和[[飓风米奇|飓风米奇]]一起并列成为有纪录以来第七强烈的大西洋飓风。首次登陆后，飓风迪安在穿过尤卡坦半岛的过程中减弱，然后进入了[[坎佩切湾|坎佩切湾]]。由于该海湾内水温较高，风暴再度短暂加强，又在[[韦拉克鲁斯州|韦拉克鲁斯州]]实现二度登陆。之后迪安朝西北方向移动，逐渐减弱成残留低气压，最终在[[美国西南部|美国西南部]]上空消散。

== 形成 ==
[[Image:Dean_as_a_Low_at_1245_UTC_on_August_12.JPG|thumb]]上的低气压最终将发展成飓风迪安，摄于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]2007年8月12日中午12点45分。]]
<!--[[Image:Dean_approaching_Lesser_Antilles_2007-08-16.JPG|thumb]] August 16, 2007, approaching the [[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]]]-->
2007年8月11日，一股强烈的东风波离开西非海岸，产生了杂乱无章的阵雨和[[雷暴|雷暴]]<ref name="TWOAT081111">{{cite report |author=Richard Knabb |date=2007-08-11 |title=August 11 Tropical Weather Outlook 15z |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2007-08-14}}</ref><ref name="TWOAT07081117">{{cite report |author=Jamie Rhome |date=2007-08-11 |title=August 11 Tropical Weather Outlook 21z |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2007-08-14}}</ref>。由于外界环境有利，东风波逐渐获得发展，于8月12日成为一股[[低气压|低气压]]<ref name="TWOAT07081211">{{cite report |author=Jamie Rhome |date=2007-08-12 |title=August 12 Tropical Weather Outlook 09z |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2007-08-14}}</ref><ref name="TWOAT07081211" />。强烈的上层东向风切变减弱了低气压的发展速度<ref name="TWOAT07081217">{{cite report |author=Daniel Brown, James Franklin|date=2007-08-12|title=August 12 Tropical Weather Outlook 21z|work=National Hurricane Center|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2007-08-14}}</ref><ref name="TWOAT07081222">{{cite report |author=Daniel Brown |date=2007-08-12 |title=August 12 Tropical Weather Outlook 03z |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2007-08-14}}</ref>，但到了8月13日，东风波的组织性已明显改善，美国国家飓风中心因此将其归类为“第四号热带低气压”，其时系统位于[[佛得角|佛得角]][[罗盘方位|西南偏西方向]]约835公里洋面<ref name="TWOAT07081311">{{cite report |author=Richard Knabb, Eric Blake |date=2007-08-13 |title=August 13 Tropical Weather Outlook 15z |work=National Hurricane Center|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2007-08-14}}</ref>。

低气压的西侧环流已经呈现出有深层[[对流|对流]]持续存在<ref name="td4disc1">{{cite web |author=Richard Knabb |date=2007-08-13 |title=Tropical Depression Four Discussion One |publisher=National Hurricane Center |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140103025005/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.001.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.001.shtml? |deadurl=no |archivedate=2014-01-03 |accessdate=2014-03-07}}</ref>。系统快速西进，位于一个深层高压脊的南面<ref name="td4disc3">{{cite web |author=Daniel Brown, James Franklin |date=2007-08-13 |title=Tropical Depression Four Discussion Three |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140103034602/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.003.shtml |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.003.shtml?}}</ref>，逐渐远离了减慢其发展速度的风切变，进入水温较高的海域上空<ref name="td4disc4">{{cite web |author=Jamie Rhome |date=2007-08-14 |title=Tropical Depression Four Discussion Four |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140103033206/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.004.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.004.shtml?}}</ref>。到了[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]8月14日下午15点，美国国家飓风中心将低气压升级为热带风暴，并以“迪恩”命名<ref name="td4disc5">{{cite web |author=Lixion Avila |date=2007-08-15 |title=Tropical Storm Dean Discussion Five |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.005.shtml? |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103021520/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.005.shtml |accessdate=2014-03-07 |archivedate=2014-01-03}}</ref>，这时风暴距其西面的[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]仍有2300公里<ref name="DeanTCR">{{cite web |author=James Franklin |date=2008-04-07 |title=Tropical Cyclone Report for Hurricane Dean |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2008-07-13 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL042007_Dean.pdf |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131012024447/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL042007_Dean.pdf |format=PDF |archivedate=2013-10-12 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。当天下午，虽然风暴的对流略有消退，但其强度仍在增大<ref name="td4disc6">{{cite web |author=Chris Landsea, Richard Knabb |date=2007-08-14 |title=Tropical Storm Dean Discussion Six |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140103034246/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.006.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.006.shtml?}}</ref>，当晚中心的对流也出现爆发。虽然风暴北面有干燥冷空气延缓结构的发展，但8月15日时系统中还是开始有[[雨带|不规则的雨带]]形成<ref name="td4disc8">{{cite web |author=Jack Beven |date=2007-08-15 |title=Tropical Storm Dean Discussion Eight |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140103024247/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.008.shtml |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.008.shtml? |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。到了上午风暴中已经有[[风眼|带眼]]形成<ref name="td4disc9">{{cite web |author=Eric Blake |date=2007-08-15 |title=Tropical Storm Dean Discussion Nine |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140103030325/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.009.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.009.shtml?}}</ref>，并在次日早上发展成一个完整的[[风眼|风眼]]<ref name="DeanTCR" />。[[协调世界时|UTC]]8月16日上午9点，美国国家飓风中心将位于巴巴多斯以东约890公里的风暴<ref name="DeanTCR" />升级成飓风迪安<ref name="td4disc12">{{cite web |author=Jack Beven |date=2007-08-16 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Twelve |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140103010432/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.012.shtml |archivedate=2014-01-03 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.012.shtml? |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

北面强烈的高压脊继续迫使迪安向西面的加勒比海行进<ref name="td4disc13">{{cite web |author=Eric Blake |date=2007-08-16 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Thirteen |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140103034923/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.013.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.013.shtml?}}</ref>。16日下午，对流带和不断增多的上层外流将风暴增强为二级飓风<ref name="td4disc14">{{cite web |author=Lixion Avila, Eric Blake |date=2007-08-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103033231/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.014.shtml |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Fourteen |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.014.shtml? |deadurl=no |archivedate=2014-01-03}}</ref>。风眼在一夜之间曾短暂消失，这可能是昼夜波动变化的一部分<ref name="td4disc15">{{cite web |author=James Franklin |date=2007-08-16 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Fifteen |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140103022029/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.015.shtml |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.015.shtml? |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no}}</ref>，但在8月17日早上又得以重新出现<ref name="td4disc16">{{cite web |author=Jack Beven |date=2007-08-17 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Sixteen |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.016.shtml? |archivedate=2014-01-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103033834/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.016.shtml |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

== 加勒比海和首度登陆 ==
<!--[[Image:Hurricane_Dean_145_81807_3-15_UTC.jpg|thumb]]]]-->
<!--[[Image:Dean_2007_1525z_aug_18.jpg|thumb]] August 18, 2007, south of the island of [[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]]]-->
{{lang|en|UTC}}8月17日上午9点30分，飓风迪安的中心通过[[马提尼克|马提尼克]]和[[圣卢西亚|圣卢西亚]]之间的圣卢西亚海峡进入加勒比海<ref name="td4disc17" />。飓风北面的[[风眼|风眼墙]]经过马提尼克上空，该[[省_(法国)|省]][[首都|首府]][[法兰西堡|法兰西堡]]的一个气象站报告了高达330毫米的降雨量<ref name="DeanTCR" />。进入加勒比海后风眼墙已经闭合，形成清晰的风眼<ref name="td4disc17">{{cite web |author=Lixion Avila |date=2007-08-17 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Seventeen |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140103014244/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.017.shtml |accessdate=2014-03-07 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.017.shtml? |archivedate=2014-01-03}}</ref>，由于由于所处环境风切变较少，[[海面温度|海面温度]]不断提高，飓风开始迅速强化<ref name="td4disc19" />。8月17日晚上，迪安已经达到三级飓风强度<ref name="td4disc18">{{cite web |author=Lixion Avila, Michelle Mainelli |date=2007-08-17 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Eighteen |work=National Hurricane Center |deadurl=no |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |archivedate=2014-01-03 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140103023600/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.018.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.018.shtml?}}</ref>。卫星图像显示，小安的列斯群岛上空保持着许多弧形气旋对流带，还有一个非常清晰的风眼<ref name="td4disc19">{{cite web |author=Lixion Avila |date=2007-08-17 |title=Hurricane Dean Special Discussion Nineteen |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140103025504/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.019.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.019.shtml?}}</ref>。当晚还有一架[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机对飓风执行了侦察任务，发现迪安已经增强为四级飓风<ref name="td4disc19a">{{cite web |author=Richard Knabb |date=2007-08-17 |title=Hurricane Dean Intermediate Advisory Nineteen 'A' |work=National Hurricane Center |deadurl=no |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2007-08-17 |archivedate=2014-01-02 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140102220433/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public_a.019.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public_a.019.shtml?}}</ref>，并且在{{lang|en|UTC}}8月18日早上6点时，风暴已经首次达到了五级飓风强度，风速每小时270公里<ref name="DeanTCR" />。随着风暴的强度和规模不断增加，各个象限的的风速半径也相应扩大<ref name="td4disc20">{{cite web |author=Richard Knabb |date=2007-08-17 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Twenty |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.020.shtml? |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103024026/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.020.shtml |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="td4disc21">{{cite web |author=Jack Beven |date=2007-08-18 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Twenty One |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.021.shtml? |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103025939/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.021.shtml |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。到了{{lang|en|UTC}}8月18日早上8点，飓风迪安直接在[[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|美国国家海洋和大气管理局]]第42059号海上[[浮标|浮标]]上空经过<ref name="td4disc20" />，测得的[[平均海水面|平均海水面]]（最高三分之一海浪的平均高度）达十米高<ref name="noaa_sea_buoy_42059">{{cite web |work=National Data Buoy Center |author=Staff Writer |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |date=2007-08-16 |title=Significant Wave Height at 42059 |accessdate=2007-08-19 |url=http://www.ndbc.noaa.gov/plot_wave.php?station=42059&meas=sght&uom=E |archivedate=2007-08-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5RCfrzm4p?url=http://www.ndbc.noaa.gov/plot_wave.php?station=42059 }}</ref>。8月18日，飓风发展出双层风眼墙<ref name = "td4disc23"/>，表明迪安正在进行[[眼墙置换|眼墙置换]]周期，风暴因此减弱成四级飓风，强度上开始出现短期波动<ref name="DeanTCR" /><ref name="td4disc22">{{cite web |author=Lixion Avila | date = 2007-08-18 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Twenty Two |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103011629/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.022.shtml |archivedate=2014-01-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.022.shtml? |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="td4disc24">{{cite web |author=Richard Knabb |date=2007-08-18 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Twenty Four |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.024.shtml? |archivedate=2014-01-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103030600/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.024.shtml |deadurl=no}}</ref>。当天下午，飓风的外流结构继续改善，众多的螺旋带也令其卫星图像非常清晰<ref name="td4disc23">{{cite web |author=Lixion Avila |date=2007-08-18 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Twenty Three |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.023.shtml? |archivedate=2014-01-03 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140103035720/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.023.shtml |deadurl=no}}</ref>。8月19日清晨，迪安的眼墙置换周期完成，并伴随有一些旋转式的摆动<ref name="td4disc25">{{cite web |author=Richard Pasch, Daniel Brown |date=2007-08-19 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Twenty Five |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140103020325/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.025.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.025.shtml? |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="td4disc26">{{cite web |author=James Franklin |date=2007-08-19 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Twenty Six |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.026.shtml? |archivedate=2014-01-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103033308/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.026.shtml |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

[[Image:Dean_20_aug_2007_1841Z.jpg|thumb]]8月20日下午18点41分左右，飓风迪安达到四级强度，这时距其登陆还有14个小时。]]

8月19日早上，风暴与其最高强度相比只有小幅减弱。迪安的中心从[[海地|海地]]以南约150公里海域经过，这时其风速在每小时220公里到230公里之间，达到四级飓风强度，并于当晚从牙买加以南仅40公里洋面经过。牙买加分别位于[[莫兰特贝|莫兰特贝]]和英格尔赛德（{{lang|en|Ingleside}}）的两个气象站都报告了高达330毫米的降雨量<ref name="DeanTCR" />，然而位于海地[[莱凯|莱凯]]的气象站却只记录到了30毫米降水<ref name="ORE_Haiti_rainfall">{{cite web |date=2007-11-08 |title=Rainfall — ORE Camp-Perrin, Cayes, Haiti - 2007 - (in inches) |publisher=Organization for the Rehabilitation of the Environment |accessdate=2008-07-02 |url=http://www.oreworld.org/images/r_in_eng/2007%20in_eng.pdf |format=PDF |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120417071447/http://oreworld.org/images/r_in_eng/2007%20in_eng.pdf |archivedate=2012-04-17 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

{{Most intense Atlantic hurricanes}}

8月19日夜间，飓风迪安再次得到加强<ref name="td4public28">{{cite web |author=Richard Knabb, Dave Roberts |title=Hurricane Dean Public Advisory Twenty Eight |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.028.shtml? |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103014754/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.028.shtml |archivedate=2014-01-03 |accessdate=2014-03-07 |date=2007-08-19}}</ref>并形成了紧密的单层风眼，表明已经完成的眼壁更换周期不但没有削弱，反而强化了风暴<ref name="td4disc28">{{cite web |author=Richard Knabb |date=2007-08-19 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Twenty Eight |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |archivedate=2014-01-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193046/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.028.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.028.shtml?}}</ref>。{{lang|en|UTC}}8月20日凌晨1点，风暴在第42056号海上浮标以南190公里处经过，浮标记录下的平均海水面有11米高<ref name="noaa_sea_buoy_42056">{{cite web |date=2007-08-20 |title=Significant Wave Height at 42056 |accessdate=2007-08-20 |url=http://www.ndbc.noaa.gov/station_page.php?station=42056 |archivedate=2007-08-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5RFTTIFj5?url=http://www.ndbc.noaa.gov/station_page.php?station=42056 |work=National Data Buoy Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration }}</ref>。8月20日早上，风暴中再度出现了同心风眼壁，但持续的时间很短。外界环境中的风切变很少，迪安继续向西行进，进入温度越来越高的水域，风暴也呈现出经典的上层[[对流层|对流层]]外流格局。美国东南部上空的[[高气压|高压系统]]仍在继续迫使风暴向西面的尤卡坦半岛逼近<ref name="td4disc29">{{cite web |author=Richard Pasch, Daniel Brown |date=2007-08-20 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Twenty Nine |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-08 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193030/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.029.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.029.shtml? |archivedate=2014-01-02 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。这天，风眼墙变得更加层次分明。顶端的云层冷却下来<ref name="td4disc30">{{cite web |author=James Franklin |date=2007-08-20 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Thirty |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-08 |archivedate=2014-01-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140102223211/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.030.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.030.shtml?}}</ref>，中心最低气压下降<ref name="td4disc31">{{cite web |author=James Franklin |date=2007-08-20 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Thirty One |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103025357/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.031.shtml |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.031.shtml?}}</ref>，其[[最大持续风速|风速]]也增大到每小时260公里，再一次达到五级飓风标准<ref name="DeanTCR" /><ref name="td4update08-20-835">{{cite web |author=Richard Knabb |date=2007-08-20 |title=Hurricane Dean Tropical Cyclone Update |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-08 |archivedate=2014-01-02 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193236/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.update.08210034.shtml |deadurl=no |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.update.08210034.shtml?}}</ref>。这时距其首度登陆的位置还有不到335公里<ref name="td4public31a">{{cite web |author=Richard Knabb Dave Roberts |date=2007-08-20 |title=Hurricane Dean Intermediate Advisory Thirty One A |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-08 |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140103022804/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public_a.031.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public_a.031.shtml?}}</ref>。

虽然许多对流带已经进入尤卡坦半岛上空，但迪安仍在继续强化直至风眼登陆时止。随着风眼从[[科斯塔玛雅|科斯塔玛雅]]（{{lang|en|Costa Maya}}）地区小镇玛哈瓦（{{lang|en|Majahual}}）附近进入墨西哥上空，美国国家飓风中心估计风暴的表层风速达到每小时280公里，迪安因此成为继1992年的[[飓风安德鲁|飓风安德鲁]]以来第一个以五级强度登陆的大西洋飓风<ref name="DeanTCR" />。与此同时，飓风风眼内一个[[投落送|投落送]]测得的数据表明其中心气压估计低至905[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，26.72[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]），令迪安成为继[[1935年劳动节飓风|1935年劳动节飓风]]和1988年的[[颶風吉爾伯特|颶風吉爾伯特]]以来登陆过的最强烈大西洋风暴，并且和飓风卡米尔与飓风米奇一起并列成为有纪录以来第七强烈的大西洋飓风<ref name="DeanTCR" />。迪安的登陆时间是{{lang|en|UTC}}8月21日上午9点，地点在墨西哥金塔纳罗奥州人口稀少的科斯塔玛雅地区，地理坐标18.7 N 87.8 W附近，带去了高达3.7至5.5米的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]<ref name="npr_july_1">{{cite web |date=2007-08-21 |author=Staff Writer |title=Hurricane Dean Weakens, Expected to Spare Texas |publisher=NPR.org |accessdate=2014-03-08 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100123155432/http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=13817871 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=13817871 |archivedate=2010-01-23}}</ref>。该州首府[[切图马尔|切图马尔]]的一个气象站报告飓风登陆期间的降雨量达到170毫米<ref name="DeanTCR" />。正如气象部门预计的那些，登陆令迪安大幅减弱，风眼消失，顶端云层也有所回暖<ref name="td4disc34">{{cite web |author=James Franklin |date=2007-08-21 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Thirty Four |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-08 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.034.shtml? |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103031433/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.034.shtml |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。陆地严重破坏了风暴的组织性，到迪安穿过尤卡坦半岛时已经削弱到只有一级飓风强度<ref name="td4public34a">{{cite web |author=James Franklin, Jamie Rhome |date=2007-08-21 |title=Hurricane Dean Intermediate Advisory Thirty Four A |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-08 |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140103022031/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public_a.034.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public_a.034.shtml?}}</ref>。

== 墨西哥湾和消亡 ==
8月21日下午，飓风迪安以一级飓风强度进入坎佩切湾，其内核结构已受到大幅扰乱<ref name="DeanTCR" />，因此海湾内的温暖[[海面温度|海面温度]]虽说令其再度形成了一个不规则的风眼<ref name="td4disc36">{{cite web |author=Lixion Avila |date=2007-08-21 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Thirty Six |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-08 |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140103033240/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.036.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.036.shtml?}}</ref>，但飓风在结构上已经无法支持之前曾达到过的强度<ref name="DeanTCR" /><ref name="td4disc37">{{cite web |author=Jack Beven |date=2007-08-22 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Thirty Seven |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-08 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.037.shtml? |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103012716/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.037.shtml |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。尽管如此，事实证明温暖的水流还是有利于风暴得到一定程度的强化，风眼也在夜间收缩，表明飓风的结构正在恢复。由于风速回升到了每小时160公里，结构上也有所改善，美国国家飓风中心将风暴重新归类为二级飓风<ref name="DeanTCR" /><ref name="td4disc38">{{cite web |author=James Franklin, Michelle Mainelli |date=2007-08-22 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Thirty Eight |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-08 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.038.shtml? |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103022456/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.038.shtml |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

风暴仍在继续增强，直到于{{lang|en|UTC}}8月22日下午16点30分在韦拉克鲁斯州东海岸小镇[[特科卢特拉|特科卢特拉]]（{{lang|en|Tecolutla}}）附近实现第二次，也是最后一次登陆，登陆点位于[[图斯潘_(韦拉克鲁斯州)|图斯潘]]东南偏南方向约65公里，古蒂埃雷斯萨莫拉（{{lang|es|Gutiérrez Zamora}}）东侧<ref name="td4update08-22-1150">{{cite web |author=James Franklin |date=2007-08-22 |title=Hurricane Dean Tropical Cyclone Update |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-08 |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103023242/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.update.08221646.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.update.08221646.shtml?}}</ref>。[[圣路易斯波托西州|圣路易斯波托西州]]小镇里奎特姆（{{lang|en|Requetemu}}）的一个气象站在飓风第二次登陆期间记录到了高达390毫米的降雨量<ref name="DeanTCR" />。迪安迅速减弱，在数小时内就失去了下层环流，并于次日接触到[[东马德雷山脉|东马德雷山脉]]时失去中层环流。风暴残留经过该山脉，以一片广阔低气压区的形式进入东[[太平洋|太平洋]]<ref name="td4disc40">{{cite web |author=Lixion Avila |date=2007-08-22 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Forty |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-08 |archivedate=2014-01-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193103/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.040.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.040.shtml?}}</ref>，然后向北漂流进入[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]南部，给[[圣迭戈县_(加利福尼亚州)|圣迭戈县]]带去了[[雷暴|雷暴]]，沃尔福德湖（{{lang|en|Lake Wohlford}}）有超过50毫米降水，[[埃斯孔迪多|埃斯孔迪多]]也在90分钟的时间里积累了50毫米降雨量<ref name="NCDC_679276">{{cite report |author=Stuart Hinson |date=2007-08-26 |title=NCDC Event Record Details 679276 |work=National Climate Data Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2008-07-02}}</ref>。残留低气压在[[南加州|南加州]]和[[亚利桑那州|亚利桑那州]]西部上空减弱，最终于8月30日消散<ref name="HPC_20070830">{{cite web | author = Jackson | date = 2007-08-30 |title=Surface Weather Map at 7:00 A.M. E.S.T. |work=National Centers for Environmental Prediction, Hydrometeorological Prediction Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-08 |archivedate=2014-01-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193050/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/dailywxmap/index_20070830.html |url=http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/dailywxmap/index_20070830.html |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

